{"article_id":"5UYGnwfvinI99V48","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Diane Russell , a former Democratic state legislator from Maine , sounded almost beside herself","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"as she stood outside the office of Sen. Susan Collins","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"( R-ME )","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"on Friday .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"She had just shepherded about a dozen sexual assault survivors through Collins ' s office","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"to share their stories .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Christine Blasey Ford and Brett Kavanaugh had presented stunning Senate testimony the day before","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"and , fairly or not , Kavanaugh ' s confirmation to the Supreme Court largely comes down to two Republican women :","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Collins and Sen. Lisa Murkowski","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"( R-AK ) .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Nobody else in the mostly white and male GOP conference seems likely to vote against him .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Most of them did not even appear to seriously consider it .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"\" She ' s a good person ! \"","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Russell said emphatically of the Maine senator .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"They might disagree on every matter of public policy ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"she said ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"but she still believed truly and deeply","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that Collins must be furious about the allegations against Kavanaugh and how Senate Republicans have handled them .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"As the Trump White House and Senate Republican leaders fight desperately","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"to hold GOP senators in line","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"to confirm Kavanaugh ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Collins is once again the fulcrum","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"on which the fate of the country rests .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"Nobody is sure what Collins is going to do .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"On Friday afternoon , she joined with Arizona Sen. Jeff Flake ' s call for further FBI investigation into the allegations against Kavanaugh","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"before a Senate floor vote is held .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"But she made no further comment on his nomination or how she would ultimately vote on his confirmation .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Collins is deliberate ,","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"she ' s reserved ,","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"and she never tips her hand .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"She makes her own choices .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Susan Collins saved Obamacare","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"- now she could stop Kavanaugh","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"Collins always finds herself in the middle of the Senate ' s most potent dramas .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"She , along with Murkowski and Sen. John McCain ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"now deceased ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"was one of the three Republicans","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"to stop Obamacare repeal in its tracks .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"She became something of a progressive icon ,","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"with takes","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"abounding after the vote","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"that it was truly the two women senators","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"who had made McCain ' s unforgettable thumbs-down possible .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"Progressives hoped to replicate the success on the Republican tax bill ,","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"but Collins ultimately became a final swing vote in favor of it .","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"Russell ,","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"who served eight years in the Maine House","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"and ran for governor this year","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"but garnered little support ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"isn ' t surprised","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"Collins has taken this long","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"to decide what to do .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"As she stood outside her senator ' s office ,","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"she was sympathetic to the position","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"Collins found herself in :","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"as one of the few Republican women in the Senate ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"who bears all the burden in a drama","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"that hinges on very difficult questions about memory , presumptions of innocence , and how victims of assault should be treated .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"\" She often is the last person","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"to make a choice ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"and whether she ' s genuinely weighing her options","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"and looking at all the facts","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"or if she ' s doing that","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"because it ' s convenient ,","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"that ' s not for me to speculate , \"","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Russell said .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"\" What I will say is ,","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"I have looked her in the eye ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"and","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"while we disagree on a whole host of issues ,","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"I know from the bottom of my toes","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"she cares deeply about Maine and about women .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"I am holding out hope","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"she ' ll do the right thing. \"","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"So is Tamara Field , a 50-year-old from Portland","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"who had just come down to Washington , DC , on Thursday night .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Field told me","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"she is a rape survivor","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"who suffered an attack earlier this summer","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"after meeting a man through an online dating app .","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"She had said in Collins ' s office","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"that she didn ' t want her 10-year-old daughter \" to live in a world","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"where reporting is a source of shame. \"","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"She told me","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"she wants to believe","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"Collins will stop Kavanaugh ' s nomination ,","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"because the alternative is almost too much to bear .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"\" If she votes yes ,","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"it ' s a complete and total betrayal of the women of the state of Maine and the women of America , \"","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"Field said .","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"\" This isn ' t court .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"The truth is ,","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"in a court of law , he would never be convicted .","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"There ' s not enough evidence , as in most rape cases .","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"However , he has called this a sham .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"He has suggested","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"it ' s a conspiracy","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"hatched by Democrats . \"","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"\" This is a sexual assault allegation , \"","depth":14},{"id":99,"text":"she continued ,","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"\" and that ' s how he has decided to respond :","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"with anger , with acidity , with ugliness .","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"That alone should convince Sen. Collins","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"he is not fit to sit on any bench . \"","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"Why Susan Collins always finds herself in the middle of Washington drama","depth":3},{"id":105,"text":"I have spoken with current Senate Republican aides , former Senate Democratic staffers , protesters outside Collins ' s office , and activists and political observers back in Maine","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"to get a full picture of the lawmaker ,","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"who has been in the Senate since 1997 .","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"I followed her closely myself during the Obamacare repeal debate .","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"A few things shone through ,","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"no matter what bias people brought with them :","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"Collins has built a reputation of integrity .","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"She genuinely feels strongly about women ' s rights .","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"She is deliberate","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"and wants to gather all the information","depth":14},{"id":115,"text":"she can","depth":14},{"id":116,"text":"before making a decision on a difficult issue .","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"She earnestly believes in bipartisanship and civil discourse .","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"\" She fits a certain Maine model , \"","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"said Amy Fried , a University of Maine political science professor","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"who has lived in the state for 20 years .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"\" An individual","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"who shows a great deal of civility ,","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"who shows great seriousness ... and some modicum of independence .","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"Or people think of that person as independent . \"","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"Jim Manley , a former aide to ex-Senate Democratic leader Harry Reid , pointed to one famous episode during the tax debate .","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"Collins hosted a bipartisan group of senators in her office","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"and they passed around a \" talking stick \" as a symbolic totem of good-faith debate","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"as each senator shared his or her views on the legislation .","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"It was \" utterly meaningless in the end , \"","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"Manley said .","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"Collins also secured a deal from Republican leader Mitch McConnell","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"to bring up an Obamacare stabilization bill","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"as she agreed to vote for the tax bill .","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"That deal later fell apart ,","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"and no stabilization bill was passed .","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"( Republicans blame the Democrats . )","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"She was looking for a middle ground","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"that isn ' t anywhere to be found in modern-day Washington .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"\" I think","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"in most or all the situations , she honestly thought","depth":14},{"id":141,"text":"she had a chance","depth":15},{"id":142,"text":"to pull it off ,","depth":15},{"id":143,"text":"and she misread the situation , \"","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"Manley said .","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"In hyper-polarized times , the Maine senator is inevitably one of the true swing votes on any serious issue .","depth":7},{"id":146,"text":"About 45 or more Republican senators would vote for just about anything","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"that President Donald Trump and Senate GOP leaders asked them to .","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"Collins is one of the few","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"who has the history , the political beliefs , and the standing","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"to make her own choice .","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"She is left with a true tug-of-war","depth":7},{"id":152,"text":"in making her decision on Kavanaugh .","depth":7},{"id":153,"text":"On the one hand , part of her independent image is being pro-choice and strongly supportive of women ' s rights","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"even when the rest of the Republican Party is not .","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"( Kavanaugh is thought to be opposed to abortion rights ,","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"though Collins has insisted otherwise . )","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"She won two-thirds of women and 31 percent of Democrats in her 2014 re-election ,","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"according to a CNN exit poll .","depth":8},{"id":159,"text":"But she also has said in the past","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"she believes","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"presidents have a right","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"to name their own Supreme Court nominees .","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"She is very focused on credentials ,","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"and Kavanaugh ' s are solid .","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"She is also very concerned with Senate procedure ,","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"and Kavanaugh ' s confirmation has been anything but regular order .","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"\" All of those brands are threatened","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"by voting for Kavanaugh , \"","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"Fried said .","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"On the other hand , \" it would be a huge step for her not to support her president ' s nominee . \"","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"Susan Collins , Christine Blasey Ford , Brett Kavanaugh and what comes next Collins reportedly set aside the whole day","depth":5},{"id":172,"text":"to watch Thursday 's riveting Ford-Kavanaugh hearing .","depth":5},{"id":173,"text":"She met Friday with five sexual assault victims from Maine .","depth":5},{"id":174,"text":"She has spent the last two weeks as the most sought-after senator in Washington","depth":6},{"id":175,"text":"- after a Wednesday Senate GOP lunch , some male senators formed a wall of bodies around Collins","depth":7},{"id":176,"text":"so she could duck onto the Senate floor","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"without taking questions .","depth":8},{"id":178,"text":"A final decision about Kavanaugh will inevitably be read as a ruling on one fundamental question ,","depth":7},{"id":179,"text":"described by Sen. Murkowski to the New York Times :","depth":7},{"id":180,"text":"Is a woman","depth":8},{"id":181,"text":"who says","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"she has been sexually assaulted ,","depth":10},{"id":183,"text":"and that with 100 percent certainty her assailant was Kavanaugh ,","depth":10},{"id":184,"text":"to be believed ?","depth":7},{"id":185,"text":"It ' s an unenviable and unfair position","depth":7},{"id":186,"text":"- again , 40-plus Republican men are prepared to support Kavanaugh ' s ascension to the Supreme Court ,","depth":8},{"id":187,"text":"while two GOP women are left undecided .","depth":8},{"id":188,"text":"But it ' s the way it is .","depth":6},{"id":189,"text":"Russell ,","depth":9},{"id":190,"text":"with protesters","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"still lingering outside Collins ' s office ,","depth":10},{"id":192,"text":"hoped","depth":8},{"id":193,"text":"Collins would be true to what she described as a long history of strong Maine women .","depth":7},{"id":194,"text":"Collins is known to revere Margaret Chase Smith , a Republican senator from Maine for much of the mid-20th century","depth":10},{"id":195,"text":"who fought McCarthyism ,","depth":10},{"id":196,"text":"and her former Senate colleague from the state , Olympia Snowe .","depth":9},{"id":197,"text":"\" We are so vehemently proud of the ladies from Maine .","depth":11},{"id":198,"text":"It is unbelievable , \"","depth":12},{"id":199,"text":"Russell said .","depth":12},{"id":200,"text":"\" She is part of that .","depth":10},{"id":201,"text":"It ' s not about her legacy .","depth":11},{"id":202,"text":"It ' s about the legacy of women in Maine","depth":12},{"id":203,"text":"that ' s in the balance .","depth":12},{"id":204,"text":"I know","depth":11},{"id":205,"text":"what it was like growing up","depth":12},{"id":206,"text":"and it wasn ' t a question :","depth":13},{"id":207,"text":"I could do anything","depth":15},{"id":208,"text":"I wanted ,","depth":15},{"id":209,"text":"because I was a girl from Maine . \"","depth":14},{"id":210,"text":"But there is something about Collins and Snowe","depth":12},{"id":211,"text":"that people might forget ,","depth":12},{"id":212,"text":"now that the latter has left the Senate","depth":11},{"id":213,"text":"and Collins is the only Maine Republican left","depth":11},{"id":214,"text":"to carry on tradition .","depth":11},{"id":215,"text":"\" For a long time , people thought of her as being above the party , \"","depth":11},{"id":216,"text":"Fried told me .","depth":11},{"id":217,"text":"\" But","depth":12},{"id":218,"text":"compared to Olympia Snowe ,","depth":13},{"id":219,"text":"when you look at","depth":14},{"id":220,"text":"when they served together ,","depth":14},{"id":221,"text":"she was more likely to be voting with Republicans . \"","depth":11},{"id":222,"text":"That is the impossible calculus for her","depth":9},{"id":223,"text":"as the world waits for Susan Collins ' s decision .","depth":9},{"id":224,"text":"Almost everyone","depth":10},{"id":225,"text":"I talked to ,","depth":10},{"id":226,"text":"from senior Republican aides to progressive activists ,","depth":9},{"id":227,"text":"seemed sympathetic to Collins ' s position .","depth":8},{"id":228,"text":"But the reality is that it will likely rest on her shoulders , as well as those of Murkowski ,","depth":8},{"id":229,"text":"whether Brett Kavanaugh is elevated to the Supreme Court .","depth":8},{"id":230,"text":"On Friday morning , protesters and sexual assault survivors were holding out hope .","depth":8},{"id":231,"text":"They believed","depth":9},{"id":232,"text":"Collins would do the right thing , in their eyes ,","depth":10},{"id":233,"text":"and reject Kavanaugh .","depth":10},{"id":234,"text":"Russell said it one more time for good measure .","depth":8},{"id":235,"text":"\" She ' s a good person . \"","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":471,"left":339,"right":470,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":339,"left":266,"right":338,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":253,"right":265,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":253,"left":241,"right":252,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":239,"right":240,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":239,"left":0,"right":238,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":238,"left":237,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":237,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":240,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":246,"right":251,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":6,"right":245,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":245,"left":243,"right":244,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":243,"left":7,"right":242,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":251,"left":247,"right":250,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":247,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250,"left":248,"right":249,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":248,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":249,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":265,"left":257,"right":264,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":257,"left":255,"right":256,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":255,"left":18,"right":254,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":254,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":21,"right":22,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":260,"right":263,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":260,"left":23,"right":259,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":258,"right":26,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":258,"left":24,"right":25,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":263,"left":27,"right":262,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":262,"left":28,"right":261,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":261,"left":29,"right":30,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":338,"left":279,"right":337,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":279,"left":267,"right":278,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":267,"left":31,"right":32,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":278,"left":276,"right":277,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":33,"right":275,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":270,"right":274,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":268,"right":269,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":268,"left":34,"right":35,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":36,"right":37,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":38,"right":273,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":271,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":39,"right":40,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":41,"right":42,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":43,"right":44,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":337,"left":285,"right":336,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":282,"right":284,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":282,"left":45,"right":281,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":46,"right":280,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":280,"left":47,"right":48,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":284,"left":49,"right":283,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":283,"left":50,"right":51,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":336,"left":306,"right":335,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":306,"left":298,"right":305,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":298,"left":290,"right":297,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":52,"right":289,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":289,"left":286,"right":288,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":53,"right":54,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":288,"left":55,"right":287,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":287,"left":56,"right":57,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":297,"left":296,"right":65,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":296,"left":291,"right":295,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":291,"left":58,"right":59,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":295,"left":294,"right":64,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":294,"left":292,"right":293,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":292,"left":60,"right":61,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":293,"left":62,"right":63,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":305,"left":303,"right":304,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":303,"left":66,"right":302,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":302,"left":67,"right":301,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":301,"left":299,"right":300,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":299,"left":68,"right":69,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":70,"right":71,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":304,"left":72,"right":73,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":335,"left":307,"right":334,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":307,"left":74,"right":75,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":334,"left":313,"right":333,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":313,"left":310,"right":312,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":310,"left":76,"right":309,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":309,"left":77,"right":308,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":308,"left":78,"right":79,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":312,"left":80,"right":311,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":311,"left":81,"right":